               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17920215-8-cd42" type="crimeDate">1st day of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920215-8-off41 t17920215-8-cd42"></join>, one piece of Scotch carpeting, value 39 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17920215-8-victim167" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Slidstone
                  <interp inst="t17920215-8-victim167" type="surname" value="Slidstone"></interp>
